OL,3,CTeen's lungs collapse after vaping
OL,4,Caddiction left him coughing up blood
OL,6,FA teenager who suffered two collapsed
OL,7,Flungs after becoming addicted to
OL,8,Fvaping is speaking out as a warning to
OL,9,Fothers.
OL,11,FNathan Chesworth, now 16, would often
OL,12,Fsmoke several 600-puff vapes a week,
OL,13,Foften buying the flavoured vapes after
OL,14,Fschool while wearing his uniform.
OL,16,FHe says the e-cigarettes were easy to
OL,17,Fget hold of, despite the legal age for
OL,18,Fusing them being 18.
