OL,3,CTeen's lungs collapse after vaping
OL,4,Caddiction left him coughing up blood
OL,6,FThe teen, studying for his GCSEs,
OL,7,Fwould frequently ask to leave class to
OL,8,Fuse the toilet so he could vape during
OL,9,Flessons.
OL,11,FNathan said: "I could go into more or
OL,12,Fless any corner shop and get one. I
OL,13,Fwould get served in my school uniform.
OL,15,F"I didn't get asked for ID or
OL,16,Fanything. I would just give them the
OL,17,Fmoney and they were like 'here you
OL,18,Fgo'."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
