OL,3,CTeen's lungs collapse after vaping
OL,4,Caddiction left him coughing up blood
OL,6,FNathan, from Wigan, had seen his GP on
OL,7,Fmultiple occasions and been prescribed
OL,8,Fantibiotics for a chest infection, and
OL,9,Fhad not told anyone about the amount
OL,10,Fof vapes he was using.
OL,12,FBut when he began coughing up blood,
OL,13,Fbecame lethargic, and was losing
OL,14,Fweight, he was rushed to hospital
OL,15,Fwhere it was discovered he had a
OL,16,Fcollapsed lung.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
