OL,3,CTeen's lungs collapse after vaping
OL,4,Caddiction left him coughing up blood
OL,6,FNathan bought the vapes with money
OL,7,Ffrom his paper round, with his parents
OL,8,Fonly discovering how heavily addicted
OL,9,Fhe was when his other lung collapsed
OL,10,Fjust two months later.
OL,12,FNathan hopes by sharing his story he
OL,13,Fcan warn others about how dangerous
OL,14,Fand easily accessible vapes really are.
OL,16,FNathan said: "Now I think, what went
OL,17,Fthrough my head to make me start doing
OL,18,Fit? To be such an idiot and start
OL,19,Fvaping and damage myself this much.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
