OL,3,CTeen's lungs collapse after vaping
OL,4,Caddiction left him coughing up blood
OL,6,F"You don't think of it when you start.
OL,7,FI just felt like I had dug a hole I
OL,8,Fcould never get out of."
OL,10,FNathan went on to pass his GCSEs and
OL,11,Fis now at college. He says he has
OL,12,Flearnt the hard way not to take his
OL,13,Fhealth for granted.
OL,15,FNone of Nathan's family smoke or vape
OL,16,Fand his mother Rebecca Chesworth
OL,17,Fthinks there needs to be more
OL,18,Fawareness around underage vaping and
OL,19,Fthe potential health risks.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
