OL,6,FRebecca said: "I think we just don't
OL,7,Fknow the long term effects of vaping
OL,8,Fand I think in years to come there
OL,9,Fwill be so much more that will come
OL,10,Fout about vaping that we never knew.
OL,12,F"I think shopkeepers and advertising
OL,13,Fcompanies need to take some
OL,14,Fresponsibility... obviously (they)
OL,15,Fneed to make money but they are more
OL,16,Fconcerned with making money than
OL,17,Fpeople's health so they are putting
OL,18,Fprofits before that young person's
OL,19,Fhealth.
