OL,6,FThe UK Vaping Industry Organisation is
OL,7,Fone of many bodies calling for more
OL,8,FGovernment funding for Trading
OL,9,FStandards to tackle the widespread
OL,10,Fissue of underage vape sales and
OL,11,Fillegal vapes.
OL,13,FAbdul Bari, Chief Trading Standards
OL,14,FOfficer for Bolton Trading Standards
OL,15,FService said: "A lot of it comes down
OL,16,Fto a lack of resources within local
OL,17,Fgovernments nationally because there
OL,18,Fhas been a lack of officers to deal
OL,19,Fwith things.
