OL,6,F"So in terms of fines - a lot of work
OL,7,Fgoes into that by creating the
OL,8,Fprosecution report and that can lead
OL,9,Fto a very small fine... which can be
OL,10,Feasily absorbed by a business..
OL,11,Fbecause they are making repeated
OL,12,Funderage sales."
OL,14,FBolton Trading Standards said despite
OL,15,Fthe demands on its resources it was
OL,16,Fdetermined to tackle the issue of
OL,17,Funderage sales and illegal vapes head
OL,18,Fon.
